;Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:20.22,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是遠山和葉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團致大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張DVD是小學館贈送給大家的特製DVD哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀看DVD時 要保持室內明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能靠電視或螢幕太近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 體溫還不算太高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天睡一天應該就能好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我幫你向學校請個假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不走就要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯的事已經和爸爸說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋好被子 安心睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs35\1c&H454A4B\bord0\shad0\pos(118,658)\frx-6\fry-2\frz-3.5\fax0.08\fsp5}米花鎮垃圾收集日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnsimhei\fs32\1c&H454A4B\bord0\shad0\pos(29,695)\fry-4\frz-3}可燃垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼頭感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他自己說是不要緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 最近新一聯繫過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甩了那個沒人性的 重找個好男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼重找啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新出醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既是醫生 又年長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定比新一靠得住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 園子那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定我就會一直這樣 變不回原來的樣子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為生病的關係嗎 思維變得消極了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點養好病…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H81CAFF\fnVrlcgcRn\fs66\fsp5}10{\fnAgalVcEG\fs73\fsp3}年後的異鄉人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個藥的解毒劑 又試製出新的成品了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個藥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,APTX4869嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 要不要試試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當…當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛從學校回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 得帶衣服過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是校服？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想突然出現在學校 嚇大家一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼做的話 要是消息傳出去怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 快開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先量量體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,38.7℃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺高的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一路跑過來的 所以才升高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎 在這種高燒下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥效和至今為止的那些藥相同 大約維持24小時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是速效的 一吃下去應該就會有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…這樣就又能變回工藤新一了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 灰原？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 那傢伙哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12點半…現在能趕在午休結束前到校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的樹有這麼高嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為和柯南的視角不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大廈我見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這公寓什麼時候建的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩視角下果然有些東西看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是這麼說的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一陣子沒見 變得好老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非在我離開的這段時間 我的鞋櫃被撤銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會嚇一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒人吃驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這些人都是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒一個認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞錯教室了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先找到蘭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她午休時常去社團活動室的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了鎖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探俱樂部？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然已經在哪吃過了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說好了 每週二跟週四要在社團活動室一起吃便當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是好不容易才忍住沒把便當早早吃光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室裡彌漫著元太的鰻魚便當的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有元太的便當裡會放鰻魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 光彥和步美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他們怎麼一副高中生的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 柯南有點奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯…柯南？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒戴眼鏡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把眼鏡取下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 這樣才像柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 靠得太近了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 離遠些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}就是說啊 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}你這算什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H40}不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副目呆口瞪的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 是目瞪口呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我問你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非我們…上高二了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:10:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概從灰原來電話開始就全都是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你擋到路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哀 又不吃中飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對身體不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用減肥 灰原同學的身材也夠好了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原 過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在應該是工藤新一 為什麼還被看作柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 為什麼你我都不是小學一年級而是高二啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你想知道這十年來發生了什麼的話 我可以告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒能和組織做個了結的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間流逝 我們升入初中 又步入了高中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:10:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用我製作的APTX4869的解毒劑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾次變回了原來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知不覺間產生了抗藥性 這五年來完全沒變回過原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來很受打擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在午休期間喪失記憶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午的課程要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你還是回家休息比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的訪問對象 是浪花的名偵探服部平次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷解決疑難案件 成為國民英雄的服部平次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次開設了自己的偵探事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大展身手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部先生有很多年輕的女性崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別名『浪花魅力男子』呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真令人高興啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼魅力男子啊 是煤黑男子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 和葉 別隨便進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 色膽包天的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遜的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說兩位 還沒結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結…結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接…接…接餛飩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也感覺舊了些啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔…一點沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來翹了下午的課吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我也沒法教訓別人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心情不好 也早退了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過著輕鬆的OL(office lady)生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 喝得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@simsun\fs40\fscy115\frz-90\bord3\shad0\pos(605,259)\c&HF6F3EE\3c&H805E5E\fsp5}淚與不捨之酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…洋子小姐也要結婚退出演藝界了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能不借酒消愁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人…淚水的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去喝啤酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都完全不以我為怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來十年來 我一直寄住在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我真的喪失記憶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到結婚 蘭好像也終於下定決心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定決心？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定結婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和新出醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新出醫生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼好吃驚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道新出醫生兩年前向蘭求婚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蘭一直等著不回來的新一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了給那份思緒一個答案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}蘭說 要去和新一留下過回憶的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我留下過回憶的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…我怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}蘭…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別點燈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓…柯南看到我哭的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…滿載著我和新一的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…結婚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和新出醫生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 不能結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我會…很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…就是工藤新一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 別結婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進了高中後 真的變得一模一樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不是什麼一模一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我打起精神 說這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這樣就讓我下定決心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經 等了十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等上十年也無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天得去和新出醫生說一聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭 我真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 柯南？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}身體好熱…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3小時20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平時短了20個小時以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次失敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…陷入幻覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了解毒劑 變回了原來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一直昏迷呻吟著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}陷入幻覺 大概是因為體溫過高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解毒劑生效需要感冒發燒的症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像燒得太厲害也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你 收集到了珍貴的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了 還是回去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新出老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝人家吧 他聽蘭說了你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地來看你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來探病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這房間真亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 這是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒也退了 應該沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你中午出去了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿中飯來的時候 你不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去廁所了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是去上廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為是病好了一些就去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能那麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 看 和我說的一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我馬上去準備晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也留下來一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}我要滿滿的一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}元太你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H30}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次變回柯南算是件好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手藝真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是又多了個大問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:05.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}回味有你陪伴的日子　樹下的光影斑斕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:16.45,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}下定決心要捨棄的事物　雖然已經不在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:26.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}思緒巡迴流轉　刹那間　依戀在身邊穿梭往返
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.80,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz90\move(50,360,80,360)}Doing all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:35.65,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}內心在搖擺　無法繼續筆直向前地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:37.70,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\move(80,360,50,360)}Doing all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:45.20,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}摸索探尋著　哪怕懷抱的是稚嫩飄渺的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:56.20,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}靜謐無風的午後　少許的安歇  還有尚未回答的問詢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:22:05.60,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,800)\frz-90\pos(40,360)}感覺一切宛如輕展雙翼　漣漪般四散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:05.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}かみしめた君の記憶　木漏れ日の匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:16.45,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}置いてきた何かはもう　此処にはないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:26.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}巡りゆく想い　するり　通り抜ける人戀しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:35.65,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}心揺らされ　振り向かずに生きれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:45.20,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}手探りして　夢見がちでもいいんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:56.20,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}風の止んだ午後　少しの自由　答えのない問いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:22:05.60,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,800)\frz-90\pos(90,360)}そっと羽ばたくように　弾けてゆく
